      "text": "Justin Compute Map\n\nSource:\ncompanies.yml\ndeals/*.yml\n\nClean schema:\n81 companies\n257 directed deals\n13 role categories\n8 deal types\n\nSurface:\nTrace | Timeline | Cluster | Search\ncompany graph\ndeal table\nprofile panel",
